{"tid":1785451,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"其實三罷上我係唔同意黃店要罷市","createTime":"2019-12-16T11:20:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T11:59:26.000Z","uid":75778,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a1377bd0715e43f41312f1d9296dac0b69865b1b","tid":1785451,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:20:38.000Z","msg":"手足真係罷工時想幫襯黃色經濟圈<br />\n但原來已經罷咗市<br />\n結果想幫襯都冇得幫<br />\n反而每當籌備三罷<br />\n黃店應該要繼續開門<br />\n等手足可以幫襯 或者有咩危急情況都可以入去避一避<br />\n如果三罷嗰日 黃店可能將當日純利3成捐比星火係仲有意義過罷市<br />\n其實你問我我係唔建議黃店將當日收益扣減成本捐哂出去<br />\n一來你嗰日開門變咗係免費奴工<br />\n二來黃色經濟圈係要賺錢 賺得更多 令小數派 藍店懷疑人生<br />\n三來賺多啲 可以請更多手足做嘢 <br />\n咁樣先係黃色經濟圈既理想發展 並唔係一味捐哂錢出去 當然你要捐哂我唔會反對你 但係可持續性先係重點<br />\n呢場係長期之戰 係考驗大家韌性既時候<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可"},{"pid":"5b715fd6a3060454c6edfb5b505e6af6d71610be","tid":1785451,"uid":213784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:21:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sdw2RCH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fsdw2RCH.jpg&h=8da8b8c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ja88Na2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fja88Na2.jpg&h=543efee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmRJ7hx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmRJ7hx.jpg&h=a821da85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咤叱歌曲投票link 👇👇👇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><a href=\"https://usca.my903.com/mobile/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fusca.my903.com%2Fmobile%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7nO0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=9973bfd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://usca.my903.com/mobile/</a></span><