cb8","tid":1785451,"uid":188685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T11:59:26.000Z","msg":"元旦倒數。。年年都係10、9、8、7、6。。。。。<br />\n今年，香港人在全球傳媒鏡頭下，<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">10、9、光、復、香、港、時、代、革、命</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">12.22  聲援新疆集會<br />\n12.24 和你shop 我要攬炒<br />\n12.31 十八區和你拖<br />\n2020.1.1  元旦遊行</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kn972fL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fkn972fL.jpg&h=d7d2f971&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L6TArHq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL6TArHq.jpg&h=46d9221e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MFstMHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMFstMHt.jpg&h=85aebd14&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QSDD8VP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQSDD8VP.jpg&h=21442a98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wcRBVAP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwcRBVAP.jpg&h=1f846dfd&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}